                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Mid-30s, quiet and observant. Works as a translator. Carries unspoken grief from a childhood loss she never fully processed. Tends to express emotion through silence and physical action rather than words. Her defining trait is an almost architectural sense of distance — she maintains careful space between herself and others as a form of self-protection.",
